actions.message:
```
mk!Help                      Lists available commands
mk!Kick [@user] [reason]     Kicks the mentioned user
mk!Ban [@user] [reason]      Bans the mentioned user
mk!Mute [@user]              Mutes the mentioned user
mk!Unmute [@user]            Unmutes the mentioned user
mk!DeleteChannel [#channel]  Deletes the mentioned channel
mk!DeleteRole [#channel]     Deletes the mentioned role
```
